## Decision Trees

When choosing between similar components, reference `.design-system-context/system/patterns/component-match.md`:

- Dialog vs Sheet vs Drawer
- Alert vs Toast vs AlertDialog
- Select vs Combobox vs RadioGroup
- Tabs vs Accordion
